[3] News update
Date: Mon 9 Aug 2021
Source: Bloomberg News [edited]
https://blinks.bloomberg.com/news/stories/QXLFTET0G1KX


Canada has extended restrictions on direct flights from India to [21 Sep 2021]. In the United States, new coronavirus cases surged to the highest weekly level since early February [2021], fueled by the highly transmissible delta variant. Deaths rose by 49%, the biggest weekly increase since December [2021]. Hospitalizations in the state of Arkansas climbed to a record. The Pentagon will require members of the US military to get vaccinated by [15 Sep 2021]. The US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention raised the travel advisory for France and Israel to the highest level. Israel is considering lowering the minimum age for a 3rd dose of the Pfizer Inc.-BioNTech SE shot to 40 or 50 from 60.

[byline: Jason Gale]

